2. Build the graph (adjacency list) and compute in-degrees for each node.
3. Initialize a min-heap with all nodes having in-degree 0.
4. While the heap is not empty:
   a. Extract the minimum element (lexicographically smallest).
   b. Add it to the result list.
   c. For each neighbor of this node:
      i. Decrement its in-degree.
